name: FriendMatch
tagline: Friend Match is a platform that finds you friends and suggests you events based on your hobbies.
body:
### Welcome to FriendMatch
Friend Match is a platform that finds you friends and suggests you events based on your hobbies.
The platform lets you explore your skills which you earlier did not have company to pursue with.

The back-end is flask server written in python and uses mySQL database and the front-end is an Android application.

### Source Code
Back-End : https://github.com/DevipriyaSarkar/FriendMatch-Backend  
Front-End : https://github.com/DevipriyaSarkar/FriendMatch-Frontend

### Try it right away
Download the Android App from [here] (https://github.com/DevipriyaSarkar/FriendMatch-Frontend/releases)

### About
DBMS Project by [Devipriya Sarkar](https://github.com/DevipriyaSarkar) and [Namita Roy](https://github.com/namitaroy63)
